      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently struggles to stay idle and exhibits noticeable smoke, while the transmission has difficulty engaging certain gears. Externally, there is widespread rust on the rocker panels and various dents throughout the bodywork. The interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This car is best suited as a project vehicle or for parts, as it is not currently in reliable driving condition.",
